<p>I love silly archives. I believe passionately in the idea that popular culture is dominant in shaping societies, and that, because of this, we must look at this type of culture in great detail. Madonna informed the way women moved in society the same way <em>The Teletubbies</em> showed children that there is an association between the color purple and a handbag when the bag is carried by a man.</p>

